  Locus:
    Page: 305
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Love
---
Try to radiate your love equally to all people instead of just a few. Try
to feel that the whole world is your Self, your God. Try to see the Self
in all people. Spread your love in all directions as an act of worship
and surrender, because everything in the world is a manifestation of God.
